pr_title: Look / Feel changes for cargotracker website
pr_body:
Refers #56 ,

The Pull Request consists of changes which include:

1) Changes to the Navigation bar
2) Text Spacing and Formatting for the website (includes line spacing, aligning etc)
3) Added Favicon and logo

pr_body:
Adds Primefaces 12.0.0 support to Cargo Tracker.

This can now be iterated upon to improve and extend functionality using the features that come along with the latest Primefaces release.

Fixes #259  ,

1) The navigation bar does not cover/hide content when the collapsible button is clicked on a resized view port, i.e the content
    below will pushed down and will be still visible.

2) The page is responsive and now does not leave empty margin spaces and consumes full view port space.

For testing purposes, link to the demo gh-pages site: https://yashtef.github.io/cargotracker/
